{"type":"text","timestamp":1777013895957,"sessionID":"ses_241d9f7b3ffeMqi0Lc2w61CcA3","part":{"id":"prt_dbe472c300025PGT9MI3ubqc2W","messageID":"msg_dbe4710d9001ADbLCvpoGjp0Ce","sessionID":"ses_241d9f7b3ffeMqi0Lc2w61CcA3","type":"text","text":"Oracle 的分析和我们刚才方向高度一致，而且它给了一个更“克制”的版本：**不要把状态枚举搞太多，重点是拆轴。**\n\n我建议我们把两版融合一下：\n\n- 用我的版本保留 capability-library 需要的 `delivery / attention / operations`\n- 用 Oracle 的版本收敛 `lifecycle`，避免状态过多\n- 把 `finite / ongoing` 明确作为最重要分叉\n\n下面是我建议的 **project-manager 项目状态 v0.3**。\n\n---\n\n# Project Status v0.3\n\n## 1. 核心原则\n\n项目状态不是一条线，而是几个维度：\n\n```text\nproject_mode        项目运行模式\nlifecycle_status    项目是否还活着\nphase               当前处在哪个项目阶段\nactivity_status     当前推进/运行状态\nhealth_status       健康度\ndelivery_status     交付/成熟度\nattention[]         需要关注的事项\noperations          持续项目的运行摘要\n```\n\n其中最核心的是前三个：\n\n```text\nproject_mode\nlifecycle_status\nphase\n```\n\n---\n\n# 2. 最关键字段：project_mode\n\n```text\nproject_mode:\n- finite\n- ongoing\n```\n\n## `finite`\n\n有限交付型项目。\n\n例如：\n\n- 做一个 CLI\n- 创建一个 skill\n- 写一篇文档\n- 完成一次调研\n- 搭一个 workflow\n- 修一个功能\n\n它可以完成：\n\n```text\nfinite -> completed\n```\n\n## `ongoing`\n\n持续运行型项目。\n\n例如：\n\n- 素材库\n- 每日新闻热点收集\n- 舆情监控\n- 定时数据采集\n- 长期知识库\n- 每周报告生成\n- agent 自动巡检\n\n它不应该标记为 `completed`，而应该长期处于：\n\n```text\nactive + operations\n```\n\n最后如果不用了，是：\n\n```text\nretired\n```\n\n不是 completed。\n\n---\n\n# 3. 生命周期状态 lifecycle_status\n\n我建议采纳 Oracle 的简化版本：\n\n```text\nproposed\nactive\npaused\ncompleted\nretired\narchived\n```\n\n但我建议加回一个 `planned`，因为你经常会有“已经决定做，但还没施工”的状态。\n\n所以 v0.3：\n\n```text\nlifecycle_status:\n- proposed\n- planned\n- active\n- paused\n- completed\n- retired\n- archived\n```\n\n## 含义\n\n| 状态 | 含义 |\n|---|---|\n| `proposed` | 已提出，尚未确定要做 |\n| `planned` | 已立项/决定做，正在设计或排计划 |\n| `active` | 正在建设、推进、运行或维护 |\n| `paused` | 暂停 |\n| `completed` | 已完成，仅适合 `finite` |\n| `retired` | 已退役，尤其适合 `ongoing` |\n| `archived` | 已归档，只保留记录 |\n\n我暂时不保留：\n\n```text\nidea\nrejected\ncancelled\nmaintenance\noperational\n```\n\n原因：\n\n- `idea` 可以视为 `proposed` 的早期。\n- `rejected/cancelled` 可以通过 `retired` 或 `archived` + reason 表达。\n- `maintenance` 更适合做 `phase`。\n- `operational` 更适合做 `phase = operations` + `activity = stable/running`。\n\n---\n\n# 4. 当前阶段 phase\n\n这里直接吸收你说的完整链路。\n\n```text\nphase:\n- intake\n- requirements\n- feasibility\n- architecture\n- planning\n- construction\n- validation\n- launch\n- operations\n- maintenance\n- retirement\n- closure\n```\n\n## 中文对应\n\n| phase | 中文 |\n|---|---|\n| `intake` | 项目录入/初始接收 |\n| `requirements` | 前期需求设计 |\n| `feasibility` | 项目可行性分析 |\n| `architecture` | 架构设计 |\n| `planning` | 施工计划/任务拆解 |\n| `construction` | 施工/建设/实现 |\n| `validation` | 验证/测试/验收 |\n| `launch` | 上线/发布/交付准备 |\n| `operations` | 持续运行 |\n| `maintenance` | 维护/修复/优化 |\n| `retirement` | 退役处理 |\n| `closure` | 关闭/归档 |\n\n我建议保留 `planning`，因为“架构设计”和“施工计划”不是一回事：\n\n- `architecture`：怎么设计系统\n- `planning`：怎么拆任务、排优先级、安排推进\n\n---\n\n# 5. 活动状态 activity_status\n\nOracle 建议：\n\n```text\nqueued\nin_progress\nblocked\nwaiting\nstable\nneeds_attention\n```\n\n我建议稍微扩展一点，以支持持续项目：\n\n```text\nactivity_status:\n- queued\n- in_progress\n- scheduled\n- stable\n- running\n- waiting\n- blocked\n- degraded\n- paused\n- needs_attention\n```\n\n## 含义\n\n| activity | 含义 |\n|---|---|\n| `queued` | 排队中，还没开始 |\n| `in_progress` | 人或 agent 正在推进 |\n| `scheduled` | 已排期/等待定时触发 |\n| `stable` | 稳定可用/稳定运行 |\n| `running` | 当前正在运行任务/周期流程 |\n| `waiting` | 等外部输入、用户、审核、资源 |\n| `blocked` | 阻塞，无法推进 |\n| `degraded` | 仍能运行，但质量下降或部分失败 |\n| `paused` | 暂停活动 |\n| `needs_attention` | 需要关注，但不一定阻塞 |\n\n如果想更细，后续可以加：\n\n```json\n\"waiting_reason\": \"user | agent | external | review | resource\"\n```\n\n不要把 waiting 拆太多放进主枚举。\n\n---\n\n# 6. 健康状态 health_status\n\n```text\nhealth_status:\n- green\n- yellow\n- red\n- gray\n```\n\n| health | 含义 |\n|---|---|\n| `green` | 正常 |\n| `yellow` | 有风险/部分异常 |\n| `red` | 明确失败/阻塞/不可用 |\n| `gray` | 信息不足，无法判断 |\n\n这个适合 dashboard。\n\n---\n\n# 7. 交付成熟度 delivery_status\n\n这个字段对 capability-library 很重要，因为“写完”和“注册可用”不是一回事。\n\n```text\ndelivery_status:\n- none\n- concept\n- draft\n- prototype\n- usable\n- delivered\n- verified\n- published\n- deprecated\n```\n\n## 含义\n\n| delivery | 含义 |\n|---|---|\n| `none` | 没有成果 |\n| `concept` | 概念/方案 |\n| `draft` | 初稿 |\n| `prototype` | 原型 |\n| `usable` | 可内部使用 |\n| `delivered` | 已交付 |\n| `verified` | 已验证 |\n| `published` | 已发布/注册/接入正式入口 |\n| `deprecated` | 已废弃 |\n\n对 `project-manager` 这种能力包：\n\n- 只有 README：`draft`\n- 有 CLI/SKILL 但没验证：`usable`\n- 通过验证：`verified`\n- 注册到 `mycli` / `skill-library`：`published`\n\n---\n\n# 8. attention[]\n\n这个用数组。\n\n基础：\n\n```text\nneeds_user_decision\nneeds_user_input\nneeds_scope_confirmation\nneeds_review\nneeds_validation\nneeds_unblock\nneeds_cleanup\nneeds_handoff\n```\n\n持续项目新增：\n\n```text\nneeds_maintenance\nneeds_operation_check\nneeds_schedule_setup\nneeds_runbook\nneeds_retirement_decision\n```\n\n示例：\n\n```json\n\"attention\": [\n  \"needs_maintenance\",\n  \"needs_operation_check\"\n]\n```\n\n---\n\n# 9. operations：持续项目运行摘要\n\n对于 `project_mode = ongoing` 的项目，建议有 `operations` 对象。\n\n```json\n\"operations\": {\n  \"cadence\": \"daily\",\n  \"trigger\": \"schedule\",\n  \"schedule_expr\": \"0 8 * * *\",\n  \"last_run_at\": \"2026-04-24T08:00:00+08:00\",\n  \"last_run_status\": \"success\",\n  \"last_success_at\": \"2026-04-24T08:00:00+08:00\",\n  \"next_run_at\": \"2026-04-25T08:00:00+08:00\",\n  \"consecutive_failures\": 0,\n  \"run_count_7d\": 7,\n  \"success_count_7d\": 7,\n  \"output_summary\": \"Collected 32 hot topics and generated daily digest.\",\n  \"runbook\": \"runbooks/daily-news.md\"\n}\n```\n\n## cadence\n\n```text\non_demand\nhourly\ndaily\nweekly\nmonthly\nevent_driven\ndaemon\nmanual\n```\n\n## trigger\n\n```text\nmanual\nschedule\nevent\nwatcher\ndaemon\nagent\nworkflow\n```\n\n## last_run_status\n\n```text\nsuccess\npartial\nfailed\nskipped\nunknown\n```\n\n这比把“运行成功/失败”塞进 `lifecycle_status` 干净得多。\n\n---\n\n# 10. 状态转移\n\n## 10.1 finite 项目主路径\n\n```text\nproposed\n-> planned\n-> active\n-> completed\n-> archived\n```\n\nphase：\n\n```text\nintake\n-> requirements\n-> feasibility\n-> architecture\n-> planning\n-> construction\n-> validation\n-> launch\n-> closure\n```\n\n如果交付后有维护：\n\n```text\ncompleted/maintenance\n-> active/maintenance\n-> active/validation\n-> completed\n```\n\n也可以生命周期保持 `completed`，phase 进入 `maintenance`，这个之后可以再细定。\n\n---\n\n## 10.2 ongoing 项目主路径\n\n```text\nproposed\n-> planned\n-> active\n-> retired\n-> archived\n```\n\nphase：\n\n```text\nintake\n-> requirements\n-> feasibility\n-> architecture\n-> planning\n-> construction\n-> validation\n-> launch\n-> operations\n-> maintenance\n-> validation\n-> operations\n...循环...\n-> retirement\n-> closure\n```\n\n最关键规则：\n\n```text\nongoing 不进入 completed\nongoing 结束时进入 retired\n```\n\n---\n\n# 11. 持续运行项目的状态例子\n\n## 每日新闻热点收集\n\n```json\n{\n  \"project\": {\n    \"id\": \"daily-hot-news\",\n    \"name\": \"每日新闻热点收集\",\n    \"type\": \"research\",\n    \"project_mode\": \"ongoing\",\n    \"domain\": \"content-ops\",\n    \"tags\": [\"daily\", \"news\", \"hot-topics\"]\n  },\n  \"status\": {\n    \"registration\": \"indexed\",\n    \"lifecycle\": \"active\",\n    \"phase\": \"operations\",\n    \"activity\": \"stable\",\n    \"health\": \"green\",\n    \"delivery\": \"published\",\n    \"attention\": [],\n    \"summary\": \"每日热点收集稳定运行。\",\n    \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-24T08:10:00+08:00\",\n    \"updated_by\": \"scheduler\"\n  },\n  \"operations\": {\n    \"cadence\": \"daily\",\n    \"trigger\": \"schedule\",\n    \"schedule_expr\": \"0 8 * * *\",\n    \"last_run_at\": \"2026-04-24T08:00:00+08:00\",\n    \"last_run_status\": \"success\",\n    \"last_success_at\": \"2026-04-24T08:00:00+08:00\",\n    \"next_run_at\": \"2026-04-25T08:00:00+08:00\",\n    \"consecutive_failures\": 0,\n    \"run_count_7d\": 7,\n    \"success_count_7d\": 7,\n    \"output_summary\": \"Collected 32 hot topics and generated daily digest.\",\n    \"runbook\": \"runbooks/daily-hot-news.md\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 部分数据源坏了\n\n```json\n\"status\": {\n  \"lifecycle\": \"active\",\n  \"phase\": \"operations\",\n  \"activity\": \"degraded\",\n  \"health\": \"yellow\",\n  \"attention\": [\"needs_maintenance\"],\n  \"summary\": \"主流程仍可运行，但微博热榜源连续失败。\"\n},\n\"operations\": {\n  \"last_run_status\": \"partial\",\n  \"consecutive_failures\": 0\n}\n```\n\n## 完全跑不起来\n\n```json\n\"status\": {\n  \"lifecycle\": \"active\",\n  \"phase\": \"maintenance\",\n  \"activity\": \"blocked\",\n  \"health\": \"red\",\n  \"attention\": [\"needs_unblock\", \"needs_maintenance\"],\n  \"summary\": \"采集流程连续失败，需要修复。\"\n},\n\"operations\": {\n  \"last_run_status\": \"failed\",\n  \"consecutive_failures\": 3\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n# 12. 素材库项目例子\n\n素材库也是 ongoing，但不一定定时运行。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"project\": {\n    \"id\": \"asset-library\",\n    \"name\": \"素材库\",\n    \"type\": \"documentation\",\n    \"project_mode\": \"ongoing\",\n    \"domain\": \"asset-management\"\n  },\n  \"status\": {\n    \"registration\": \"indexed\",\n    \"lifecycle\": \"active\",\n    \"phase\": \"operations\",\n    \"activity\": \"stable\",\n    \"health\": \"green\",\n    \"delivery\": \"usable\",\n    \"attention\": [],\n    \"summary\": \"素材库可用，按需持续补充。\"\n  },\n  \"operations\": {\n    \"cadence\": \"on_demand\",\n    \"trigger\": \"manual\",\n    \"last_run_status\": \"unknown\",\n    \"runbook\": \"runbooks/asset-library.md\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n这里 `stable` 比 `idle` 更合适，因为素材库处于“稳定可用”状态，不是“没人管”。\n\n---\n\n# 13. 推荐最终字段结构\n\n```json\n{\n  \"project\": {\n    \"id\": \"project-manager\",\n    \"name\": \"Project Manager\",\n    \"type\": \"capability\",\n    \"project_mode\": \"finite\",\n    \"domain\": \"agent-system-rules\",\n    \"root\": \"D:\\\\agent_workspace\\\\capability-library\\\\agent-system-rules\\\\project-manager\",\n    \"owner\": \"千束\",\n    \"tags\": []\n  },\n  \"status\": {\n    \"registration\": \"registered\",\n    \"lifecycle\": \"planned\",\n    \"phase\": \"requirements\",\n    \"activity\": \"waiting\",\n    \"health\": \"green\",\n    \"delivery\": \"concept\",\n    \"attention\": [\"needs_user_decision\"],\n    \"summary\": \"Designing project status model with support for ongoing projects.\",\n    \"updated_at\": \"2026-04-24T00:00:00+08:00\",\n    \"updated_by\": \"assistant\"\n  },\n  \"current\": {\n    \"goal_id\": \"goal-0001\",\n    \"task_id\": \"task-0001\",\n    \"next_action_id\": \"next-0001\",\n    \"summary\": \"Confirm project status v0.3.\"\n  },\n  \"operations\": null\n}\n```\n\n对于 `finite` 项目：\n\n```json\n\"operations\": null\n```\n\n对于 `ongoing` 项目：\n\n```json\n\"operations\": {...}\n```\n\n---\n\n# 14. 我建议现在锁定的 v0.3 枚举\n\n```text\nproject_mode:\n  finite | ongoing\n\nlifecycle:\n  proposed | planned | active | paused | completed | retired | archived\n\nphase:\n  intake | requirements | feasibility | architecture | planning |\n  construction | validation | launch | operations | maintenance |\n  retirement | closure\n\nactivity:\n  queued | in_progress | scheduled | stable | running |\n  waiting | blocked | degraded | paused | needs_attention\n\nhealth:\n  green | yellow | red | gray\n\ndelivery:\n  none | concept | draft | prototype | usable |\n  delivered | verified | published | deprecated\n\noperation.last_run_status:\n  success | partial | failed | skipped | unknown\n```\n\n---\n\n# 15. 关键约束\n\n必须写进规则里：\n\n1. `project_mode = ongoing` 不应进入 `completed`。\n2. `project_mode = ongoing` 的正常长期状态是：\n   ```text\n   lifecycle = active\n   phase = operations\n   activity = stable / running / scheduled\n   ```\n3. `project_mode = ongoing` 停止服务应进入：\n   ```text\n   lifecycle = retired\n   phase = retirement\n   ```\n4. `completed` 只用于 `finite`。\n5. `archived` 是只读归档态。\n6. `phase = maintenance` 不代表项目失败，只表示当前工作是维护。\n7. `activity = degraded` 表示还在运行，但质量下降或部分失败。\n8. `operations` 只对 ongoing 必填，对 finite 可为空。\n\n---\n\n# 16. 我的建议\n\n我建议我们就以 v0.3 为基础继续往下设计。\n\n下一步可以设计三件事之一：\n\n1. `project.json` schema；\n2. `status.md` 展示模板；\n3. `next_actions` / 推进项模型。\n\n如果按依赖顺序，我建议先做：\n\n```text\nproject.json schema\n```\n\n因为状态模型需要先落成结构化 schema，后面注册、查询、状态更新都依赖它。","time":{"start":1777013828656,"end":1777013895956}}}
